  Title   : Computer Car Pit Strategy - MPS Grand Prix (IBM)
  Keywords: PIT STRATEGY TSR RACING FREEWARE F1GP WC IBM WORLD CIRCUIT

  CCPIT V3.0 is a TSR which modifies the behaviour of MPS Grand Prix.
  CCPIT allows you to specify the number of stops the computer cars should
  make and on which lap(s). CCPIT has been tested with V1.05 of both the US
  and European versions of GP.EXE. Freeware contributed by the author Trevor
  Kellaway (CIS:100331,2330). This is not an MPS product. Requires PKUNZIP
  2.04g to decompress. 

